Class Invite

java.lang.Object
database.model.BaseEntity
database.model.entities.Invite
public class Invite extends BaseEntity
Represents an invitation in the system, including a random invite code, associated user ID, roles, and the creation timestamp.

This class generates a unique invite code and associates it with a user and roles. It also stores the creation timestamp in seconds.

Author:
Dhruv
